high_descs: Turn left and go to the stove ahead.
Pick up the pot on the stove.
Turn left and go straight until you reach the sink, then turn right to face it.
Wash the pot in the sink.
Turn around, go toward the wall, then turn left to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the pot inside, and close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pot in the fridge.

high_descs: Pick up pot from bottom left burner of stove.
Turn left, proceed to sink on right.  Turn right to face sink.
Place pot in left side of sink, fill sink with water, empty water, pick up pot.
Turn around, proceed to wall.  Turn left, proceed to refrigerator.
Open refrigerator, put pot on top right shelf, close refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Clean pot and put it in refrigerator.

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen stove on your left.
Pick up the pot from the stove.
Walk to the kitchen sink on the left.
Put the pot in the sink, wash the pot, and grab it again.
Walk to the fridge behind you and to your right.
Put the pot in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Clean a pot and store it in the fridge.
